summary:
Croatian Software Engineer with a strong affection for solving challenging, complex problems and working on innovative engineering projects. I hold a masters degree in Software Engineering & GreenIT from VU and UvA (joint degree) universities in Amsterdam. 

Skills:
Kotlin (functional programming style oriented) + Arrow.kt, GraphQL, Redis, RediSearch, Java + Spring (Boot), REST OpenAPI spec design and implementation, Azure Cloud, Kubernetes, MSSQL, PostgreSQL, Spring Reactor, Google Cloud Platform, serverless, scripting, CI/CD optimization and more...
